
package javaday6;

import java.util.Scanner;



public class OddNum extends Thread
{
    @Override
	public void run() {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		super.run();
	
	Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
	
	int n=sc.nextInt();
	
	for(int i=0;i<=n;i++)
	{
		if(i%2!=0)
			System.out.println(i);
	}

}
}
